		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014/paper08.html">A Metamodel Family for Role-Based Modeling and Programming Languages</a></em> (<a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html"><span class="info">Thomas Kühn</span></a>, <a href="../profile/MaxLeuthäuser.html">Max Leuthäuser</a>, <a href="../profile/SebastianGötz.html">Sebastian Götz</a>, <a href="../profile/ChristophSeidl.html">Christoph Seidl</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2015/index.html">SLE 2015</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2015/paper04.html">A combined formal model for relational context-dependent roles</a></em> (<a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html"><span class="info">Thomas Kühn</span></a>, <a href="../profile/StephanBöhme.html">Stephan Böhme</a>, <a href="../profile/SebastianGötz.html">Sebastian Götz</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2016/index.html">SLE 2016</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2016/paper12.html">FRaMED: Full-Fledge Role Modeling Editor (Tool Demo)</a></em> (<a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html"><span class="info">Thomas Kühn</span></a>, <a href="../profile/KayBierzynski.html">Kay Bierzynski</a>, <a href="../profile/SebastianRichly.html">Sebastian Richly</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>)</li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2017/index.html">SLE 2017</a>)</span> Served on <a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2017/sle-2017-papers-artifact-evaluation-committee">AEC</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2018/index.html">SLE 2018</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2018/paper12.html">Continuous model validation using reference attribute grammars</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JohannesMey.html">Johannes Mey</a>, <a href="../profile/RenéSchöne.html">René Schöne</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/EmmaSöderberg.html">Emma Söderberg</a>, <a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html"><span class="info">Thomas Kühn</span></a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html">Niklas Fors</a>, <a href="../profile/JesperÖqvist.html">Jesper Öqvist</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>)</li>
