<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2018s/index.html">SLE 2018 SI</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2018s/paper01.html">Relational Reference Attribute Grammars: Improving continuous model validation</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JohannesMey.html">Johannes Mey</a>, <a href="../profile/RenéSchöne.html">René Schöne</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/EmmaSöderberg.html">Emma Söderberg</a>, <a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html"><span class="info">Thomas Kühn</span></a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html">Niklas Fors</a>, <a href="../profile/JesperÖqvist.html">Jesper Öqvist</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>)</li>
